    "description": "<p>You have a remarkably strong immune system and are impervious to most ordinary sicknesses.</p><p><strong>Level 1:</strong> Your maximum System Strain increases by 2 points, up to a maximum of 20. You gain a +4 bonus on all saving throws versus diseases, and any diseases you incur are reduced one level of severity, with Mild diseases automatically resisted.</p><p><strong>Level 2:</strong> As level 1, but your maximum System Strain increases by a further +2 to a maximum of 22. You are immune to all normal diseases.</p>",
